# Claude Rules for Victor Uhnger Portfolio

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 16 (App Router)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 4 (ALWAYS use pure Tailwind classes, NEVER use CSS variables like `var(--color-purple)`)
- **UI Components**: Shadcn/ui
- **Animations**: Framer Motion
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Icons**: react-icons

## Color Scheme (Tailwind utilities)
- Primary: `text-purple`, `bg-purple`, `border-purple` (#c770f0)
- Secondary: `text-ocean`, `bg-ocean`, `border-ocean` (#4A90E2)
- Accent: `text-accent-green`, `bg-accent-green` (#D2DCB6)
- Use variants: `-light` and `-dark` for each color

## Design Principles
- Dark theme (black background)
- Bento-box card layout
- Minimalistic and clean
- Everything should fit on one screen (no unnecessary scrolling)
- Norwegian language for content

## Development Workflow
1. Always use Tailwind CSS utilities (never `var(--color-*)`)
2. Make git commits after completing features
3. Use Norwegian for UI text and labels
4. Keep components simple and focused

